About NSL

It is a small language like c, so we call it c--.
We can use it to descript the jump state.
for example:

/*
state init{
    unsigned name:8
	printf("hello\n");
	goto state1;
}
state state1{
	  printf("world\n");
}
*/
program-> block | state_block
state_block->{stc|cts id : block} | block
block->{decls stmts}
decls -> decls decl | e
decl -> unsigned id:number
stmts -> stmts stmt | e

stmt-> loc = bool;
       |if (bool)stmt
       |if (bool)stmt else stmt
       |while(bool)stmt
       |do stmt while(bool);
       |block
